      "message": "readability: if this block goes into its own function `allocateInvocations`, and below code is combined into `enqueuBatchOfInvocations` then this func gets easier to read and cleanup doesn\u0027t need to be copied.\n\nassertInTransaction(c)\ninvs, err :\u003d e.allocateInvocations(c, job, req)\nif err \u003d\u003d nil {\n   err \u003d e.enqueuBatchOfInvocations(c, job, invs)\n}\nif err !\u003d nil {\n  // Best effort cleanup.\n  e.cleanupInvocationsAfterFail(c, invs)\n  return nil, transient.Tag.Apply(err)\n}\nreturn invs, nil",
